functionDescription: This function creates a new Lua object, initializes its properties, and links it to the global state for garbage collection management.

inputInterfaces.name: tt
inputInterfaces.meaning: Type tag of the new object

inputInterfaces.name: offset
inputInterfaces.meaning: Offset for the new object in memory

outputInterfaces.name: o
outputInterfaces.meaning: Pointer to the newly created garbage collectible object

outputInterfaces.name: ret
outputInterfaces.meaning: Return pointer to the new object
